title: Ep. 8 - Self Respect  & The Impostor Syndrome
itunes:title: Ep. 8 - Self Respect  & The Impostor Syndrome
description:
"The only respect that matters is self respect"
In this episode we talk about getting rid of your self limiting beliefs. We also speak about something called the "impostor syndrome" which is a psychological phenomenon in which people are unable to internalize their accomplishments.
